Altuzarra - The soft-pink hue of Altuzarra's Henri trousers brings to mind outdoor celebrations in balmier months. They're crafted in Italy from ultra-lightweight wool that's blended for a touch of stretch and shaped to flattering slim legs, which are cropped and zipped at the ankle. Style yours with the matching blazer and white heels for an alternative summer-wedding edit.
